                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890708-20-off97 t17890708-20-crimeloc99"></join>; on the 26th of June I lost two cloaks, I was in Ship-alley at the time; when I came home my wife and son told me the house was robbed; the prisoner was taken the next evening.</p>
